# 🧹 Cleaned E-Commerce Dataset — De-Code Labs

A cleaned and analysis-ready e-commerce orders dataset containing **1,200 transactions** spanning **January 2023 to June 2025**, prepared as part of the De-Code Labs Data Analytics project.

## 📄 File

`Cleaned_Dataset_DeCodeLabs.xlsx`

---

## ✅ Cleaning Summary

- **Zero null values** across all 14 columns (missing `CouponCode` values from the raw dataset have been filled)
- Consistent formatting applied to all categorical fields
- Date column standardized to datetime format
- Ready for EDA, visualization, or machine learning pipelines

---

## 📐 Dataset Overview

| Property | Details |
|----------|---------|
| **Rows** | 1,200 orders |
| **Columns** | 14 |
| **Date Range** | Jan 1, 2023 – Jun 30, 2025 |
| **Null Values** | None |

---

## 🗂️ Column Reference

| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| `OrderID` | String | Unique order identifier (e.g. `ORD200000`) |
| `Date` | Date | Date the order was placed |
| `CustomerID` | String | Unique customer identifier (e.g. `C72649`) |
| `Product` | Categorical | Product category ordered |
| `Quantity` | Integer | Number of units ordered (1–5) |
| `UnitPrice` | Float | Price per unit in USD |
| `ShippingAddress` | String | Delivery address |
| `PaymentMethod` | Categorical | Method used to pay |
| `OrderStatus` | Categorical | Current status of the order |
| `TrackingNumber` | String | Shipment tracking reference |
| `ItemsInCart` | Integer | Total items in cart at checkout (1–10) |
| `CouponCode` | Categorical | Discount code applied at checkout |
| `ReferralSource` | Categorical | Channel that referred the customer |
| `TotalPrice` | Float | Final order value in USD (`Quantity × UnitPrice`) |

